text: Nataliya Zyatikova (born 5 May 1974) is a Belarusian cross-country skier. She competed in five events at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Belarus Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kemerovo Category:Sportspeople from Kemerovo Oblast
